### Listar todas
  GET http://localhost/reservas_ms/reservas

  ### Por vehículo
  GET http://localhost/reservas_ms/reservas?vehiculo_id=1

  ### Por cliente
  GET http://localhost/reservas_ms/reservas?cliente_id=1

  ### Crear reserva
  POST http://localhost/reservas_ms/reservas
  Content-Type: application/json

  {"vehiculo_id":1,"cliente_id":1,"fecha_inicio":"2026-06-01","fecha_fin":"2026-06-05"}

  ### Cancelar
  PUT http://localhost/reservas_ms/reservas?id=1
  Content-Type: application/json

  {"estado":"cancelada"}